Date-Components version 0.2.1
=======================


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES



This module requires these other modules and libraries:

     warnings              1.05
     version               0.74
     Carp                  1.04
     Readonly              1.03
     Test::More            0.74
     Test::Manifest        1.22
     Test::Pod             1.26
     Test::Pod::Coverage   1.08


   Install but do NOT use.  Readonly accesses it to improve performance
     Readonly::XS  1.04  




